VERSION 1.4
=============
With v1.4 the following changes were introduced:

All files:
==========

1) INCLUDE fragments have been replaced by INCLUDE properties.

2) Fragment *group* syntax ( [[ and ]] ) has been removed

errorscreen.bet:
================

1) New file containing pattern corresponding to the standard error
   stream (errorscreen)

iostate.bet:
============

1) New file containing interface to UNIX file descriptors.
   Used with systemenv.